1
00:00:04,120 --> 00:00:05,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Asa.</i></font>

2
00:00:06,160 --> 00:00:09,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Your name was chosen
 with a great deal of care.</i></font>

3
00:00:09,110 --> 00:00:14,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>It embodies the beauty of all new things
 that come with each day.</i></font>

4
00:00:15,860 --> 00:00:20,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I wish with all my heart that you'll 
be loved by everyone around you.</i></font>

5
00:00:21,480 --> 00:00:26,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>And I'll do everything I can 
to make that come true.</i></font>

6
00:00:29,040 --> 00:00:34,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Asa, as your mother, I...</i></font>

7
00:00:30,250 --> 00:00:31,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Arial"><font size="16">{\an8}<font color="#3f392e">Asa's Personal Belongings</font></font></font></font>

8
00:00:42,890 --> 00:00:49,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<font face="Georgia"><font size="18"><font color="#3b3132">Journal with Witch</font></font></font></font>

9
00:02:08,910 --> 00:02:10,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ah, hey there.</font>

10
00:02:10,950 --> 00:02:13,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sorry about all the trouble.</font>

11
00:02:13,990 --> 00:02:15,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}No worries.</font>

12
00:02:14,270 --> 00:02:19,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font size="12"><font face="Georgia">{\an3}<font color="#ffffff">Episode 7\h\h<font size="18">Leave in Writing</font></font></font></font></font>

13
00:02:15,120 --> 00:02:17,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}I'll have an iced caffè latte, please.</font>

14
00:02:17,250 --> 00:02:18,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Coming right up.</font>

15
00:02:20,170 --> 00:02:21,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}How's Makio-san been?</font>

16
00:02:20,170 --> 00:02:21,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So how's Makio doing?</font>

17
00:02:22,630 --> 00:02:25,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, we can talk about her later.</font>

18
00:02:25,480 --> 00:02:26,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah.</font>

19
00:02:27,130 --> 00:02:30,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">By the way, I had no idea 
you'd changed jobs.</font>

20
00:02:30,250 --> 00:02:31,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yup, a year ago.</font>

21
00:02:31,800 --> 00:02:34,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So I've got no connections and no 
foundation to get me anywhere.</font>

22
00:02:34,970 --> 00:02:38,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I feel bad leaning on you like this.</font>

23
00:02:38,270 --> 00:02:40,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, I'm always happy to help.</font>

24
00:02:40,700 --> 00:02:45,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">To cut to the chase, they seem 
really excited to meet you.</font>

25
00:02:45,420 --> 00:02:46,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nice!</font>

26
00:02:46,780 --> 00:02:50,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They seem to have a similar vision,
 so I think I can arrange something.</font>

27
00:02:51,180 --> 00:02:52,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What do you say?</font>

28
00:02:52,090 --> 00:02:53,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A casual meetup, or...?</font>

29
00:02:53,250 --> 00:02:56,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nah, I want to dive right into business.</font>

30
00:02:56,400 --> 00:03:00,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Gotcha. Then let me give 
you their contact info.</font>

31
00:03:00,280 --> 00:03:01,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thanks a bunch!</font>

32
00:03:02,240 --> 00:03:04,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I haven't been to a family-style 
restaurant in ages.</font>

33
00:03:04,640 --> 00:03:07,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They're great for bringing kids along.</font>

34
00:03:07,790 --> 00:03:10,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Can I call you Makio-san?</font>

35
00:03:11,010 --> 00:03:14,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank you for making time today.</font>

36
00:03:14,550 --> 00:03:16,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, sure.</font>

37
00:03:16,650 --> 00:03:20,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We've known Asa-chan since
 they were in elementary school.</font>

38
00:03:17,910 --> 00:03:20,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}We've got to get the parfait!</font>

39
00:03:20,190 --> 00:03:21,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Strawberry or chocolate?</font>

40
00:03:20,190 --> 00:03:23,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I was friendly with her parents 
for quite a while.</font>

41
00:03:21,590 --> 00:03:23,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Um, I dunno... I can't decide!</font>

42
00:03:23,450 --> 00:03:24,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I see...</font>

43
00:03:23,620 --> 00:03:24,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}You'll have some too, right?</font>

44
00:03:24,910 --> 00:03:25,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}For sure.</font>

45
00:03:25,450 --> 00:03:31,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">To be honest, I still haven't really 
processed that they're gone.</font>

46
00:03:25,870 --> 00:03:27,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Then let's get one of each.</font>

47
00:03:27,080 --> 00:03:28,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Let's do it!</font>

48
00:03:31,580 --> 00:03:34,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's all just so sudden, isn't it?</font>

49
00:03:35,930 --> 00:03:40,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Anyway, when you didn't shown up 
for graduation or the entrance ceremony,</font>

50
00:03:40,200 --> 00:03:42,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">it had me worried about 
what kind of person you might be.</font>

51
00:03:43,280 --> 00:03:53,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<font face="Impact"><font color="#b3b9ba">The shameless sort</font></font></font>

52
00:03:43,800 --> 00:03:47,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I apologize for causing you concern...</font>

53
00:03:47,810 --> 00:03:50,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, no! I'm sorry.</font>

54
00:03:50,260 --> 00:03:53,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You see, I heard all about you
from Emiri and Asa-chan afterward.</font>

55
00:03:53,720 --> 00:03:56,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I understand now 
that you're perfectly fine!</font>

56
00:03:56,850 --> 00:04:01,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">When you put it like that, 
I worry that I'm not fine at all.</font>

57
00:04:01,060 --> 00:04:03,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But I'm trying my best...</font>

58
00:04:03,970 --> 00:04:06,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's what it means to raise a child.</font>

59
00:04:08,840 --> 00:04:10,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm glad I met you today.</font>

60
00:04:11,470 --> 00:04:15,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wait, so Makio-san didn't
mention anything to you?</font>

61
00:04:15,100 --> 00:04:17,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nope, I haven't seen her in a while.</font>

62
00:04:17,110 --> 00:04:20,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hang on, does this mean something's 
happened between you two?</font>

63
00:04:20,770 --> 00:04:22,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Like what? Fess up.</font>

64
00:04:22,610 --> 00:04:26,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Er, but you're her best friend.</font>

65
00:04:26,480 --> 00:04:28,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If she hasn't told you, I dunno if I...</font>

66
00:04:28,110 --> 00:04:31,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'd never talk romance with her. Gross.</font>

67
00:04:31,270 --> 00:04:34,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And "best friend"? Blegh!</font>

68
00:04:34,230 --> 00:04:37,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah, your friendship's 
always been weird like that.</font>

69
00:04:37,910 --> 00:04:39,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Y'know, Kasamachi-kun...</font>

70
00:04:39,640 --> 00:04:44,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Back in the day, <i>you</i> were the one
 who wanted to be introduced to <i>us</i>.</font>

71
00:04:44,140 --> 00:04:47,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If you'd never said anything, 
I doubt we ever would've met.</font>

72
00:04:44,880 --> 00:04:50,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><b><font size="14"><font face="Comic Sans MS"><font color="#3a3939">Huh.</font></font></font></b></font>

73
00:04:45,380 --> 00:04:50,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an3}<b><font size="14"><font face="Comic Sans MS"><font color="#3a3939">What's "huh"
 supposed to mean?</font></font></font></b></font>

74
00:04:45,880 --> 00:04:55,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><b><font size="14"><font face="Comic Sans MS"><font color="#3a3939">So, where?</font></font></font></b></font>

75
00:04:46,640 --> 00:04:55,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<b><font size="14"><font face="Comic Sans MS"><font color="#3a3939">Someone I met at the bar 
introduced us.</font></font></font></b></font>

76
00:04:47,640 --> 00:04:55,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><b><font size="14"><font face="Comic Sans MS"><font color="#3a3939">Wait,
 Toritetsu?</font></font></font></b></font>

77
00:04:47,730 --> 00:04:49,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">N-Not ever?</font>

78
00:04:47,890 --> 00:04:55,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><b><font size="14"><font face="Comic Sans MS"><font color="#3a3939">Hey, I like your ring.</font></font></font></b></font>

79
00:04:48,640 --> 00:04:55,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><b>{\an8}<font size="14"><font face="Comic Sans MS"><font color="#3a3939">Yup.</font></font></font></b></font>

80
00:04:49,140 --> 00:04:55,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><b>{\an8}<font size="14"><font face="Comic Sans MS"><font color="#3a3939">You know Masuda?</font></font></font></b></font>

81
00:04:49,630 --> 00:04:54,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thinking back on it, 
I could never keep up with you guys.</font>

82
00:04:49,640 --> 00:04:55,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><b><font size="14"><font face="Comic Sans MS"><font color="#3a3939">You mean
 Kesami.</font></font></font></b></font>

83
00:04:49,890 --> 00:04:55,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><b><font size="14"><font face="Comic Sans MS"><font color="#3a3939">What?</font></font></font></b></font>

84
00:04:50,140 --> 00:04:55,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an9}<b><font size="14"><font face="Comic Sans MS"><font color="#3a3939">So, what are 
they up to?</font></font></font></b></font>

85
00:04:50,390 --> 00:04:55,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><b><font size="14">{\an1}<font face="Comic Sans MS"><font color="#3a3939">Wait, I didn't 
know that.</font></font></font></b></font>

86
00:04:50,890 --> 00:04:54,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><b><font size="14"><font face="Comic Sans MS"><font color="#3a3939">{\an3}I haven't even logged in
 to Facebook in forever.</font></font></font></b></font>

87
00:04:51,390 --> 00:04:55,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><b><font size="14"><font face="Comic Sans MS"><font color="#3a3939">Get this.</font></font></font></b></font>

88
00:04:51,890 --> 00:04:55,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an1}<b><font size="14"><font face="Comic Sans MS"><font color="#3a3939">Hey, Kasamachi looks
 like that one dude.</font></font></font></b></font>

89
00:04:52,640 --> 00:04:55,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><b><font size="14"><font face="Comic Sans MS"><font color="#3a3939">I think we're thinking
 of the same one.</font></font></font></b></font>

90
00:04:53,390 --> 00:04:55,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><b><font size="14"><font face="Comic Sans MS"><font color="#3a3939">Stop talking shit.</font></font></font></b></font>

91
00:04:54,140 --> 00:04:55,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><b><font size="14"><font face="Comic Sans MS"><font color="#3a3939">I haven't even said
 anything yet.</font></font></font></b></font>

92
00:04:54,330 --> 00:04:55,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I know.</font>

93
00:04:54,890 --> 00:04:55,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><b><font size="14"><font face="Comic Sans MS"><font color="#3a3939">I know you're 
about to talk shit.</font></font></font></b></font>

94
00:04:56,400 --> 00:04:58,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So, what's the scoop?</font>

95
00:04:59,340 --> 00:05:02,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I didn't think you'd be very happy.</font>

96
00:05:03,010 --> 00:05:05,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If I got close to her again, I mean.</font>

97
00:05:07,080 --> 00:05:12,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">In my family, my dad never 
said a word when we went out.</font>

98
00:05:12,150 --> 00:05:14,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It was like he was there all by himself.</font>

99
00:05:14,370 --> 00:05:15,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, man.</font>

100
00:05:15,940 --> 00:05:17,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}I hated that.</font>

101
00:05:17,460 --> 00:05:19,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Your dad was kind of a quiet guy.</font>

102
00:05:17,500 --> 00:05:21,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She talks about her parents a lot.</font>

103
00:05:19,990 --> 00:05:22,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}He never really had much to say.</font>

104
00:05:21,950 --> 00:05:24,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I sometimes wonder if 
she's sharing too much.</font>

105
00:05:24,780 --> 00:05:26,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It took me by surprise at first.</font>

106
00:05:27,110 --> 00:05:31,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But maybe it's better for her 
to talk about things openly.</font>

107
00:05:32,480 --> 00:05:34,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That might be true.</font>

108
00:05:35,210 --> 00:05:38,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I wasn't in contact with my sister, so...</font>

109
00:05:39,520 --> 00:05:41,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, hey. Mom.</font>

110
00:05:41,700 --> 00:05:43,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What now?</font>

111
00:05:43,580 --> 00:05:44,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Excuse me.</font>

112
00:05:44,850 --> 00:05:47,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Can I go buy swimsuits with Asa?</font>

113
00:05:47,100 --> 00:05:48,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You already have swimsuits.</font>

114
00:05:48,690 --> 00:05:50,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}But I'm too tall for them now.</font>

115
00:05:50,300 --> 00:05:51,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Really?</font>

116
00:05:51,700 --> 00:05:53,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}How much have you grown?</font>

117
00:05:51,930 --> 00:05:54,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's that face for?</font>

118
00:05:53,560 --> 00:05:54,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Five centimeters.</font>

119
00:05:54,220 --> 00:05:55,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I wanna buy some too.</font>

120
00:05:54,830 --> 00:05:56,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}What? Fine, I suppose.</font>

121
00:05:55,200 --> 00:05:57,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wait, don't you have swimsuits too?</font>

122
00:05:56,850 --> 00:05:57,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Yay.</font>

123
00:05:57,840 --> 00:05:59,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Like you would know!</font>

124
00:05:59,740 --> 00:06:02,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's entirely not the point.</font>

125
00:06:02,960 --> 00:06:04,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm too tall for mine too, okay?</font>

126
00:06:04,570 --> 00:06:06,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Only by, like, two centimeters.</font>

127
00:06:06,000 --> 00:06:08,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Emiri, you traitor!</font>

128
00:06:08,450 --> 00:06:10,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wait, what? You were depressed?</font>

129
00:06:10,880 --> 00:06:13,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">After Makio-san and I split up.</font>

130
00:06:13,230 --> 00:06:18,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No way. You mean back when
 I sent you that enraged text?</font>

131
00:06:18,730 --> 00:06:21,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's terrible. I'm sorry!</font>

132
00:06:21,090 --> 00:06:25,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, no, it wasn't because 
of the split or your text.</font>

133
00:06:25,890 --> 00:06:29,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I just realized I couldn't work 
at the bank anymore.</font>

134
00:06:29,990 --> 00:06:31,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Really?</font>

135
00:06:31,400 --> 00:06:32,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I promise.</font>

136
00:06:33,880 --> 00:06:36,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wow... I didn't expect that.</font>

137
00:06:36,110 --> 00:06:38,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Not from you, though that might be rude.</font>

138
00:06:38,860 --> 00:06:39,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I get it.</font>

139
00:06:40,960 --> 00:06:44,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Honestly, I couldn't believe it myself.</font>

140
00:06:44,620 --> 00:06:48,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay, then I'll make a note 
for 5,000 yen in the cloud.</font>

141
00:06:48,260 --> 00:06:49,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">All right!</font>

142
00:06:49,260 --> 00:06:51,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What cloud?</font>

143
00:06:51,070 --> 00:06:55,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We keep notes in the cloud so we can 
share it like a bulletin board.</font>

144
00:06:55,520 --> 00:06:57,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Since I tend to forget things.</font>

145
00:06:57,880 --> 00:06:59,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You forget things?</font>

146
00:06:59,670 --> 00:07:01,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, I do.</font>

147
00:07:01,340 --> 00:07:03,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Like what kind of things?</font>

148
00:07:03,040 --> 00:07:04,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">U-Um, well...</font>

149
00:07:05,320 --> 00:07:08,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Anything, I guess.</font>

150
00:07:08,150 --> 00:07:10,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We fought about that the other day.</font>

151
00:07:10,780 --> 00:07:12,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That wasn't a fight.</font>

152
00:07:13,020 --> 00:07:14,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What a great idea.</font>

153
00:07:15,520 --> 00:07:17,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A friend gave me the advice.</font>

154
00:07:18,450 --> 00:07:21,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's 'cause Makio-chan 
can't stay organized.</font>

155
00:07:21,450 --> 00:07:25,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}She doesn't listen either. 
And she forgets even when she does.</font>

156
00:07:25,050 --> 00:07:29,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Hey, do you think she could be,
 like, neurodivergent?</font>

157
00:07:25,440 --> 00:07:26,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's no wonder.</font>

158
00:07:27,340 --> 00:07:30,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You became a parent overnight.</font>

159
00:07:29,900 --> 00:07:31,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}What's that?</font>

160
00:07:30,140 --> 00:07:31,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It must've been a huge change.</font>

161
00:07:32,200 --> 00:07:33,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, I suppose.</font>

162
00:07:34,330 --> 00:07:36,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Though it's not like I'm her mother.</font>

163
00:07:36,500 --> 00:07:39,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But it's not like she's my mom...</font>

164
00:07:41,320 --> 00:07:43,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Still, you made the decision, didn't you?</font>

165
00:07:43,970 --> 00:07:46,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">To parent Asa-chan.</font>

166
00:07:46,560 --> 00:07:49,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No, I'll never be her parent.</font>

167
00:07:49,820 --> 00:07:51,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nor am I trying to.</font>

168
00:07:51,850 --> 00:07:53,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Although I am her guardian.</font>

169
00:07:54,490 --> 00:07:58,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'd just start crying and couldn't move.</font>

170
00:07:58,890 --> 00:08:01,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I kept thinking, "Why me?"</font>

171
00:08:01,330 --> 00:08:03,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">"It's up to you to make it work."</font>

172
00:08:03,330 --> 00:08:04,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">"Get over it."</font>

173
00:08:04,460 --> 00:08:06,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">"You must not be trying hard enough."</font>

174
00:08:06,510 --> 00:08:10,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I never said it out loud, 
but I'd judge other people that way.</font>

175
00:08:10,500 --> 00:08:13,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And it all came back to bite me.</font>

176
00:08:13,800 --> 00:08:18,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Until then, I never imagined myself 
being in a position of need.</font>

177
00:08:19,760 --> 00:08:21,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I was too arrogant.</font>

178
00:08:22,060 --> 00:08:24,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You told Makio about this?</font>

179
00:08:24,410 --> 00:08:25,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Only recently.</font>

180
00:08:25,920 --> 00:08:29,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I couldn't tell anyone 
until after I changed jobs.</font>

181
00:08:29,020 --> 00:08:32,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And I was scared of how 
she might react, but...</font>

182
00:08:32,720 --> 00:08:34,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Did you sleep lots?</font>

183
00:08:34,030 --> 00:08:37,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah, I slept a ton.</font>

184
00:08:37,030 --> 00:08:39,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Then... that's good.</font>

185
00:08:39,780 --> 00:08:40,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That was it.</font>

186
00:08:40,560 --> 00:08:42,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That idiot!</font>

187
00:08:42,780 --> 00:08:46,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No, I realized I was anxious for nothing.</font>

188
00:08:46,120 --> 00:08:47,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It was a huge relief.</font>

189
00:08:47,680 --> 00:08:50,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's the side of her 
I fell for, you know?</font>

190
00:08:50,200 --> 00:08:51,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Gosh.</font>

191
00:08:51,700 --> 00:08:53,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My, my. How sweet.</font>

192
00:08:53,660 --> 00:08:55,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I-I should get going...</font>

193
00:08:55,320 --> 00:08:58,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hold up! At least tell me how it started.</font>

194
00:08:58,360 --> 00:09:03,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, I don't think that's true. 
As long as you love her...</font>

195
00:09:04,960 --> 00:09:06,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No, um, I didn't mean...</font>

196
00:09:07,360 --> 00:09:09,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How do I word this?</font>

197
00:09:10,080 --> 00:09:15,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Her parents were the people
who raised her until now.</font>

198
00:09:15,670 --> 00:09:17,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No one can replace them.</font>

199
00:09:17,690 --> 00:09:19,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Not that I know what
 they were like as parents.</font>

200
00:09:20,710 --> 00:09:24,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I wonder what Mom was really like.</font>

201
00:09:24,520 --> 00:09:30,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But now, she has no way of receiving 
what they would have bestowed upon her.</font>

202
00:09:31,460 --> 00:09:33,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Both for better and for worse.</font>

203
00:09:34,710 --> 00:09:38,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Loneliness, despair...</i></font>

204
00:09:38,800 --> 00:09:44,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>How hard it must be not to know
 the words to express those things yet.</i></font>

205
00:09:45,280 --> 00:09:48,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>The harsh truth is that 
we're never able to.</i></font>

206
00:09:48,880 --> 00:09:51,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>And we live in fear of it forever.</i></font>

207
00:09:52,540 --> 00:09:58,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's why I believe we'll have to make do
with what little she's already been given.</font>

208
00:09:58,360 --> 00:10:02,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I might be able to protect her,
but not raise her.</font>

209
00:10:02,790 --> 00:10:04,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A-Are you okay?</font>

210
00:10:05,300 --> 00:10:06,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ew.</font>

211
00:10:06,160 --> 00:10:08,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're crying again?</font>

212
00:10:08,170 --> 00:10:11,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't worry. She's the type 
to get weepy over commercials.</font>

213
00:10:11,850 --> 00:10:13,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Emiri's mom kinda reminds 
me of a chihuahua!</font>

214
00:10:13,970 --> 00:10:16,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We're off to go shopping.</font>

215
00:10:16,530 --> 00:10:18,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm sorry! Gracious...</font>

216
00:10:18,420 --> 00:10:19,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">N-No, you're fine.</font>

217
00:10:20,340 --> 00:10:23,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Just imagining if it were me
 got me going.</font>

218
00:10:23,980 --> 00:10:25,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Right...</font>

219
00:10:27,430 --> 00:10:31,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Um, can I ask you 
something, Michiko-san?</font>

220
00:10:32,400 --> 00:10:34,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, you mean me?</font>

221
00:10:34,350 --> 00:10:38,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Gosh, I get called "Emiri's mom" so much,
you caught me off guard.</font>

222
00:10:38,910 --> 00:10:40,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Please, ask away.</font>

223
00:10:41,420 --> 00:10:44,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What was my sister like?</font>

224
00:10:45,320 --> 00:10:46,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A lawyer?</font>

225
00:10:46,670 --> 00:10:49,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The guy who's watching out for Asa-san.</font>

226
00:10:49,560 --> 00:10:51,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh. Never heard of him.</font>

227
00:10:51,360 --> 00:10:54,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You see, he's good-looking.</font>

228
00:10:54,620 --> 00:10:58,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And unlike me, he's got 
this cool vibe going on.</font>

229
00:10:58,190 --> 00:11:00,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So I got a bit ahead of myself.</font>

230
00:11:00,470 --> 00:11:02,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Makio doesn't like pretty boys, though.</font>

231
00:11:02,630 --> 00:11:05,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But she likes smart guys, right?</font>

232
00:11:05,590 --> 00:11:08,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you talking about yourself, 
smarty pants?</font>

233
00:11:08,350 --> 00:11:11,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A lawyer's gotta be smarter than me.</font>

234
00:11:11,090 --> 00:11:13,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wait. You're, like, actually jealous?</font>

235
00:11:13,790 --> 00:11:15,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's not that.</font>

236
00:11:15,540 --> 00:11:18,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But Makio-san's popular with guys.</font>

237
00:11:18,220 --> 00:11:20,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I couldn't just stand back and watch.</font>

238
00:11:20,480 --> 00:11:21,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?!</font>

239
00:11:21,870 --> 00:11:23,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>That</i> pain in the ass?</font>

240
00:11:23,830 --> 00:11:26,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Only weirdos are into her!</font>

241
00:11:26,020 --> 00:11:27,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">W-Weirdos?</font>

242
00:11:27,860 --> 00:11:30,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm talking about you, damn it!</font>

243
00:11:30,180 --> 00:11:31,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Daigo-san, your voice!</font>

244
00:11:32,010 --> 00:11:33,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Minori-san...</font>

245
00:11:33,690 --> 00:11:36,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I referred to her 
as Asa-chan's mom myself.</font>

246
00:11:36,710 --> 00:11:39,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I guess I'd say she was 
pretty hard on herself.</font>

247
00:11:40,190 --> 00:11:43,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It was like she had very high standards.</font>

248
00:11:43,460 --> 00:11:44,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah...</font>

249
00:11:44,670 --> 00:11:45,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, you.</font>

250
00:11:46,010 --> 00:11:47,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You can't do something this simple?</font>

251
00:11:48,780 --> 00:11:50,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's so easy.</font>

252
00:11:50,950 --> 00:11:53,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah... Why can't I do it?</font>

253
00:11:54,760 --> 00:11:56,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I see.</font>

254
00:11:56,650 --> 00:11:59,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Perhaps you're alike in that sense.</font>

255
00:12:00,200 --> 00:12:02,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You seem hard on yourself too.</font>

256
00:12:02,250 --> 00:12:03,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Going out on a limb here.</font>

257
00:12:05,900 --> 00:12:11,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Um, did you ever hear why
 she never legally got married?</font>

258
00:12:12,020 --> 00:12:13,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Actually...</font>

259
00:12:13,720 --> 00:12:16,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I only found out from the news.</font>

260
00:12:16,600 --> 00:12:19,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I wonder if Asa-chan knew...</font>

261
00:12:20,470 --> 00:12:21,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm not sure.</font>

262
00:12:24,350 --> 00:12:27,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Somehow, it's like I hardly knew her.</font>

263
00:12:27,970 --> 00:12:34,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You know, people who knew me before 
I was a parent might say the same thing.</font>

264
00:12:34,460 --> 00:12:37,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We never know the whole truth, I suppose.</font>

265
00:12:38,680 --> 00:12:40,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Do you have any regrets?</font>

266
00:12:41,450 --> 00:12:43,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">About becoming a parent?</font>

267
00:12:44,660 --> 00:12:46,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Of course.</font>

268
00:12:46,020 --> 00:12:50,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But I'm sure I'd have regrets 
no matter the path I chose.</font>

269
00:12:50,610 --> 00:12:52,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">At this point, I'm okay with my choice.</font>

270
00:12:54,670 --> 00:12:58,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I wonder if I'd regret it more 
if I hadn't taken her in.</font>

271
00:12:58,460 --> 00:13:00,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I think you would have.</font>

272
00:13:00,600 --> 00:13:02,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Since you seem hard on yourself.</font>

273
00:13:04,460 --> 00:13:07,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm not <i>that</i> sincere.</font>

274
00:13:09,990 --> 00:13:13,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Georgia"><font size="18"><font color="#000000">Journal with Witch</font></font></font></font>

275
00:13:13,980 --> 00:13:15,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, Emiri?</font>

276
00:13:15,570 --> 00:13:16,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hmm?</font>

277
00:13:16,870 --> 00:13:21,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I heard from Sakurai-kun a while ago
 that Shinozaki asked you out.</font>

278
00:13:22,270 --> 00:13:23,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You didn't say yes?</font>

279
00:13:24,400 --> 00:13:26,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sakurai told you that?</font>

280
00:13:26,500 --> 00:13:28,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wait, how do you even know Shinozaki?</font>

281
00:13:28,400 --> 00:13:30,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We were on the same team for field day.</font>

282
00:13:30,480 --> 00:13:33,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh. Well, I'm not going out with him.</font>

283
00:13:33,100 --> 00:13:34,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What? Why not?</font>

284
00:13:34,770 --> 00:13:36,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">'Cause I don't like him.</font>

285
00:13:36,170 --> 00:13:37,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't you want a boyfriend?</font>

286
00:13:37,450 --> 00:13:39,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Maybe <i>you're</i> the one who wants one.</font>

287
00:13:39,830 --> 00:13:41,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I do, but...</font>

288
00:13:41,700 --> 00:13:45,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Band is enough fun for now. I just wanna
 hear about other people's love lives.</font>

289
00:13:45,360 --> 00:13:47,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Not cool.</font>

290
00:13:47,240 --> 00:13:48,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Seriously, though—</font>

291
00:13:48,720 --> 00:13:51,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm done talking about this. 
I don't want a boyfriend. End of story.</font>

292
00:13:51,720 --> 00:13:52,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So, what?</font>

293
00:13:52,970 --> 00:13:54,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You'd be cool with a girlfriend then?</font>

294
00:13:58,240 --> 00:14:00,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're getting on my nerves.</font>

295
00:14:00,030 --> 00:14:01,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I told you I'm done with this.</font>

296
00:14:01,560 --> 00:14:03,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Come on, you're being like Makio-chan.</font>

297
00:14:03,760 --> 00:14:06,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I tried asking her about Kasamachi-kun 
and she was the same way.</font>

298
00:14:06,880 --> 00:14:08,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah, because you're prodding.</font>

299
00:14:08,800 --> 00:14:10,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nuh-uh.</font>

300
00:14:10,240 --> 00:14:11,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Makio-chan's just weird like that.</font>

301
00:14:13,440 --> 00:14:16,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I may be completely
 off the mark, but here.</i></font>

302
00:14:17,240 --> 00:14:20,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>No matter who you fall in love with, 
or who you don't...</i></font>

303
00:14:20,240 --> 00:14:22,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's a story about how there's 
nothing wrong with that.</font>

304
00:14:25,020 --> 00:14:28,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, I'm not weird or anything.</font>

305
00:14:28,240 --> 00:14:29,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's what I mean.</font>

306
00:14:29,270 --> 00:14:31,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So it's weird that you're acting like her.</font>

307
00:14:31,890 --> 00:14:33,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">See how that's weird?</font>

308
00:14:36,400 --> 00:14:40,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I thought Asa-san would be 
home. Is this too much?</font>

309
00:14:40,150 --> 00:14:41,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We'll eat the rest tomorrow.</font>

310
00:14:41,730 --> 00:14:44,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She said she's having 
dinner with a friend.</font>

311
00:14:44,770 --> 00:14:47,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I told her to stay out of trouble.</font>

312
00:14:47,050 --> 00:14:48,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Trouble, huh?</font>

313
00:14:48,920 --> 00:14:50,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, that reminds me...</font>

314
00:14:51,160 --> 00:14:53,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an7}<font face="Arial"><font size="10"><font color="#363636">Bento Box Notes</font></font></font></font>

315
00:14:51,640 --> 00:14:53,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is for you. A bento journal.</font>

316
00:14:54,320 --> 00:14:56,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's my mom's. For some recipe ideas.</font>

317
00:14:57,290 --> 00:14:59,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can't accept someone else's journal!</font>

318
00:14:59,030 --> 00:15:01,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's really only about bento boxes.</font>

319
00:15:01,780 --> 00:15:03,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No way. Absolutely not. No.</font>

320
00:15:03,320 --> 00:15:05,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Fine, you can just borrow it.</font>

321
00:15:05,210 --> 00:15:06,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm digging in.</font>

322
00:15:08,720 --> 00:15:12,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Reading other people's handwriting 
takes a lot of energy...</font>

323
00:15:12,180 --> 00:15:14,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Like it feels too raw?</font>

324
00:15:14,040 --> 00:15:16,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah. Oh, look.</font>

325
00:15:16,380 --> 00:15:20,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">"Shingo's been hiding it, but he seems 
to like sweetened pink cod flakes."</font>

326
00:15:20,290 --> 00:15:22,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't think I was hiding that.</font>

327
00:15:22,470 --> 00:15:24,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She seems really well organized.</font>

328
00:15:24,930 --> 00:15:26,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She's pretty chill now.</font>

329
00:15:26,810 --> 00:15:29,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Always out and about with her friends.</font>

330
00:15:29,240 --> 00:15:31,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Then this must have been 
her way of showing love.</font>

331
00:15:32,940 --> 00:15:37,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">In her case, she thought showering 
me with her idea of "perfect"</font>

332
00:15:37,960 --> 00:15:41,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">would turn me into 
the perfect son she wanted.</font>

333
00:15:41,960 --> 00:15:43,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">At least deep down.</font>

334
00:15:43,620 --> 00:15:46,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't know if that's love.</font>

335
00:15:46,990 --> 00:15:50,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, only she would really know.</font>

336
00:15:51,030 --> 00:15:53,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And how you take it is up to you.</font>

337
00:15:56,500 --> 00:15:59,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You know, my sister kept a journal too.</font>

338
00:15:59,820 --> 00:16:00,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A journal?</font>

339
00:16:00,860 --> 00:16:06,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It felt wrong, but I took a peek 
inside to see if I should keep it.</font>

340
00:16:06,870 --> 00:16:08,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Turns out it was for Asa.</font>

341
00:16:08,460 --> 00:16:11,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You mean she was writing to Asa-san?</font>

342
00:16:11,100 --> 00:16:15,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah. You could say this bento 
journal was written for you too.</font>

343
00:16:17,160 --> 00:16:19,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But my sister's was more... personal.</font>

344
00:16:20,930 --> 00:16:25,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She wrote she was planning to give 
it to Asa when she turns twenty.</font>

345
00:16:25,630 --> 00:16:28,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That sounds more like a letter.</font>

346
00:16:28,450 --> 00:16:31,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I know. I didn't read 
any further than that.</font>

347
00:16:32,090 --> 00:16:34,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But she was never one to write.</font>

348
00:16:35,300 --> 00:16:40,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can't figure out what drove 
her to do so much of it.</font>

349
00:16:41,630 --> 00:16:44,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">After all, writing is a lonely process.</font>

350
00:16:45,630 --> 00:16:47,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Maybe that was love too.</font>

351
00:16:49,090 --> 00:16:54,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">In the end, my sister could've
 chosen not to give it to Asa</font>

352
00:16:54,650 --> 00:16:56,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">had she lived another five years.</font>

353
00:16:56,460 --> 00:16:57,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's true.</font>

354
00:16:57,660 --> 00:17:01,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But now that she's gone, 
you've got to give it to her.</font>

355
00:17:01,120 --> 00:17:02,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">When?</font>

356
00:17:03,130 --> 00:17:04,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">When she turns twenty?</font>

357
00:17:05,940 --> 00:17:09,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But Asa is longing for her mother now.</font>

358
00:17:10,480 --> 00:17:13,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">In a sense, her mom's still 
alive in that journal.</font>

359
00:17:14,720 --> 00:17:17,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Asa might want to read it now.</font>

360
00:17:17,700 --> 00:17:21,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Maybe it should be up 
to her when she reads it.</font>

361
00:17:22,050 --> 00:17:25,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Then it's a question of timing.
 That's tough.</font>

362
00:17:26,250 --> 00:17:27,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Seriously?</i></font>

363
00:17:28,280 --> 00:17:30,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>You're the one who got yourself killed.</i></font>

364
00:17:34,060 --> 00:17:37,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>In a sense, her mom's still 
alive in that journal.</i></font>

365
00:17:37,830 --> 00:17:39,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Seriously?</i></font>

366
00:17:39,140 --> 00:17:41,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>You went and died on your own.</i></font>

367
00:17:41,730 --> 00:17:43,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>And now this journal?</i></font>

368
00:17:43,870 --> 00:17:47,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Mom and Makio-chan both hid it from me.</i></font>

369
00:17:48,110 --> 00:17:49,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Screw you.</i></font>

370
00:17:50,830 --> 00:17:52,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Screw you.</i></font>

371
00:17:54,480 --> 00:17:55,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Screw you.</i></font>

372
00:17:56,970 --> 00:17:58,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Screw you!</i></font>

373
00:18:02,970 --> 00:18:05,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Arial"><font size="16">{\an8}<font color="#3f392e">Asa's Personal Belongings</font></font></font></font>

374
00:18:04,710 --> 00:18:07,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Come on, you're going to be late.</font>

375
00:18:07,980 --> 00:18:09,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay, okay.</font>

376
00:18:09,280 --> 00:18:10,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't say it twice like that.</font>

377
00:18:10,980 --> 00:18:12,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay.</font>

378
00:18:13,730 --> 00:18:15,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I fixed your bedhead.</font>

379
00:18:15,240 --> 00:18:16,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Have a good day.</font>

380
00:18:16,480 --> 00:18:17,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm off!</font>

381
00:18:19,220 --> 00:18:24,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My little brother says he won't get 
married because he can't be selfless.</font>

382
00:18:24,100 --> 00:18:25,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's so self-centered!</font>

383
00:18:25,450 --> 00:18:27,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Has he never worked with people?</font>

384
00:18:27,000 --> 00:18:28,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My little sister might be like that too.</font>

385
00:18:28,980 --> 00:18:30,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Really? Even as a woman?</font>

386
00:18:30,320 --> 00:18:33,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I told her she shouldn't be that way
 and got a chair thrown at me.</font>

387
00:18:33,700 --> 00:18:35,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You sure she's not a man?</font>

388
00:18:37,020 --> 00:18:40,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But when I think about it, 
she might be better off than me.</font>

389
00:18:41,300 --> 00:18:44,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She's following her heart, 
working hard on her own.</font>

390
00:18:44,100 --> 00:18:45,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Shut up!</font>

391
00:18:46,450 --> 00:18:49,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're the one who'll suffer like this.</font>

392
00:18:49,110 --> 00:18:51,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You only care about how people see you.</font>

393
00:18:51,770 --> 00:18:54,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You have nothing you like or want to do.</font>

394
00:18:54,030 --> 00:18:55,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No principles to stand by!</font>

395
00:18:55,420 --> 00:18:57,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No curiosity, no inquisitiveness, no nothing!</font>

396
00:18:57,810 --> 00:19:00,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Just because you don't have
 anything that's yours...</font>

397
00:19:01,190 --> 00:19:04,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Stop pushing your emptiness onto others!</font>

398
00:19:05,410 --> 00:19:10,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I never really cared much for kids, but
 once I had my own, it felt meant to be.</font>

399
00:19:10,650 --> 00:19:12,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So you like raising kids?</font>

400
00:19:12,790 --> 00:19:17,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's more like... I finally became 
who I always wanted to be.</font>

401
00:19:17,740 --> 00:19:19,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I've always gotten by okay.</font>

402
00:19:19,930 --> 00:19:21,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Or I thought I had.</font>

403
00:19:21,910 --> 00:19:25,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But before I knew it, 
nothing was going the way I wanted.</font>

404
00:19:25,960 --> 00:19:29,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My life didn't turn out 
anything like I imagined it.</font>

405
00:19:30,180 --> 00:19:33,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't want to get married.</font>

406
00:19:33,590 --> 00:19:37,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But... I want to take care of the child.</font>

407
00:19:38,430 --> 00:19:41,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll do the best I can as a father.</font>

408
00:19:42,580 --> 00:19:44,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If that's okay.</font>

409
00:19:45,500 --> 00:19:47,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh... Sure.</font>

410
00:19:49,020 --> 00:19:51,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah, thanks.</font>

411
00:19:51,770 --> 00:19:54,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>...where a truck struck 
a parked passenger car.</i></font>

412
00:19:55,370 --> 00:20:01,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>According to the police, its occupants
were Hajime Takumi and Minori Koudai.</i></font>

413
00:20:01,470 --> 00:20:04,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>They were taken to the hospital
but passed away.</i></font>

414
00:20:04,410 --> 00:20:05,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How's newlywed life?</font>

415
00:20:05,980 --> 00:20:09,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nothing new except for my name.</font>

416
00:20:09,380 --> 00:20:11,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">All we did was turn in some paperwork.</font>

417
00:20:11,880 --> 00:20:13,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's the whole point!</font>

418
00:20:13,850 --> 00:20:15,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How about you, Minori?</font>

419
00:20:15,000 --> 00:20:16,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're the last one left.</font>

420
00:20:16,860 --> 00:20:18,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Who would've thought?</font>

421
00:20:18,760 --> 00:20:21,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Whatever happened 
with that guy you're dating?</font>

422
00:20:21,200 --> 00:20:24,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Actually, I was just going 
to share the news today.</font>

423
00:20:24,710 --> 00:20:30,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wow, so you're finally graduating too!</font>

424
00:20:30,310 --> 00:20:34,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I've always been normal 
like everyone else.</i></font>

425
00:20:31,190 --> 00:20:32,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Congrats!</font>

426
00:20:34,500 --> 00:20:36,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I'd even say I was a bit ahead.</i></font>

427
00:20:36,760 --> 00:20:39,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Being different meant being weird.</i></font>

428
00:20:39,040 --> 00:20:39,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey.</font>

429
00:20:40,210 --> 00:20:42,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why can't you do something this simple?</font>

430
00:20:42,980 --> 00:20:44,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Answer me.</font>

431
00:20:45,460 --> 00:20:46,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Little sister of mine,</i></font>

432
00:20:47,190 --> 00:20:52,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>how do you endure being 
different from everyone else?</i></font>

433
00:20:53,430 --> 00:20:54,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Asa...</font>

434
00:20:55,000 --> 00:20:58,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your name was chosen
 with a great deal of care.</font>

435
00:20:58,400 --> 00:21:03,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It embodies the beauty of all new things
 that come with each day.</font>

436
00:21:04,640 --> 00:21:08,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I wish with all my heart that you'll 
be loved by everyone around you.</font>

437
00:21:09,400 --> 00:21:12,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And I'll do everything I can 
to make that come true.</font>

438
00:21:13,670 --> 00:21:19,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Right now, I have no idea who you'll 
become or what decisions you'll make.</i></font>

439
00:21:19,650 --> 00:21:22,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>And I may not yet know 
for many years to come.</i></font>

440
00:21:22,920 --> 00:21:27,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>But as long as you can love yourself,</i></font>

441
00:21:27,810 --> 00:21:30,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I believe that's enough.</i></font>

442
00:21:30,340 --> 00:21:35,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>It was like gazing into a giant, dark pit.</i></font>

443
00:21:36,150 --> 00:21:38,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Lying at the bottom was a monstrous fear.</i></font>

444
00:21:39,070 --> 00:21:43,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>The thought that perhaps...</i></font>

445
00:21:43,950 --> 00:21:47,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>my mom never really loved me.</i></font>

446
00:21:49,440 --> 00:21:53,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Asa, as your mother, I...</font>

447
00:21:53,950 --> 00:21:55,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Arial"><font size="48">{\an1}<font color="#252419">love you so much.</font></font></font></font>

448
00:21:57,550 --> 00:21:59,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You don't know that!</font>

449
00:21:59,960 --> 00:22:01,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It could be a lie.</font>

450
00:22:01,710 --> 00:22:03,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Who knows?</font>

451
00:22:03,960 --> 00:22:05,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She could've written anything...</font>

452
00:22:05,960 --> 00:22:07,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How would I know?</font>

453
00:22:08,130 --> 00:22:09,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How would I know?!</font>

